# ----------------------------------------
# 🔹 CHAPA PAYMENT GATEWAY
# ----------------------------------------
# ⚠️ IMPORTANT: You need the "Test Secret Key" NOT the "Test Public Key"
# 
# From: https://dashboard.chapa.co/dashboard/profile/profile/api
# You will see 3 keys:
#   1. Test Public Key  (CHAPUBK_TEST-...) ❌ NOT THIS ONE
#   2. Test Secret Key  (CHASECK_TEST-...) ✅ USE THIS ONE
#   3. Encryption Key   (Optional)
#
# Replace the value below with your "Test Secret Key":
CHAPA_SECRET_KEY="CHASECK_TEST-your_secret_key_here"

